Our occupational health and safety governance and policies The Environmental Protection, Health Management, and

Safety (EHS) department manages health and safety mea- sures at Siemens. It is organized locally, integrated into each business unit and each regional company, and reports directly to the respective business manager.

Siemensâ€™ suppliers commit to upholding the Siemens Group Code of Conduct for Suppliers and Third-Party Intermediaries and Business Partners. This Code of Conduct obligates our suppliers to comply with health and safety standards and to take responsibility for the health and well-being of their employees.